addAdmin(address).details: Any admin can add or remove other admins, careful.

params.migratorAddress: The WrappedERC20 token address that will be migrate the token
params.tokenAddress: The ERC20 token address that will be migrated using the migrator

calculateChargeBack(address,address,uint.details: No need to be extra careful as this is only a view function

params.amount: The amount of the liquidity token to be migrated(simulated)
params.liquidityPairFrom: The pair address that will be migrated from(simulated)
params.liquidityPairTo: The pair address that will be migrated to(simulated)

returns.amount0: Amount of token0 will be charged back after the migration
returns.amount1: Amount of token1 will be charged back after the migration

returns._0: Whether or not the account address is an admin.

migrateLiquidity(address,address,address.details: This function assumes sender already gave approval to move the assets

params.amount: The amount of token liquidityPairFrom that will be migrated
params.deadline: The deadline limit that should be met, otherwise revert to prevent front-run
params.liquidityPairFrom: The pair address to be migrated from
params.liquidityPairTo: The pair address to be migrated to
params.to: The address that will receive the liquidity and the charge backs

params.amount: The amount of token liquidityPairFrom that will be migrated
params.deadline: The deadline limit that should be met, otherwise revert to prevent front-run
params.liquidityPairFrom: The pair address to be migrated from
params.liquidityPairTo: The pair address to be migrated to
params.r: by passing param for the permit validation
params.s: by passing param for the permit validation
params.to: The address that will receive the liquidity and the charge backs
params.v: by passing param for the permit validation

params.amount: The amount of the token to be migrated
params.deadline: The deadline limit that should be met, otherwise revert to prevent front-run
params.to: The address of who's receiving the token
params.token: The ERC20 token address that will be migrated
